.  Our new notation will result in a list for each part reduced to an indexed concatenation, so the trick is to break up the original list into explicitly concatenated sublists before doing these reductions.  Here I’ll do it by hand, copy & pasting, and inserting “} ⧺ {” before/after every reducible subsequence:
